            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Which operators can we use to make comparisons for if statement conditions?</p><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\"><code>&gt;=</code>, <code>&lt;=</code>, <code>&gt;</code>, <code>&lt;</code>, <code>==</code>, and <code>!=</code></item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\">Only <code>==</code> and <code>!=</code></item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\"><code>&gt;=</code>, <code>&lt;=</code>, <code>&gt;</code>, <code>&lt;</code>, <code>==</code>, and <code>!=</code>.</p></body></html>"
