            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Which of these data types can we compare using <code>==</code> in conditions?</p><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\">Integers, floats, strings, and booleans</item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\">Only integers and strings</item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Integers, floats, strings, and booleans.</p></body></html>"
