            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>How can we avoid rewriting the same comparison multiple times?</p><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\">We can save its result in a variable and reuse the variable</item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\">We can't avoid it since comparisons can't be saved for later</item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">We can save its result in a variable and reuse the variable.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: Good decisions",
            "id": 123824,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Code a condition that runs the code if <code>replay_times</code> is greater than or equal to <code>300</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"song = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Don't stop me now&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"replay_times = \" /><text value=\"345\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" replay_times &gt;= \" /><text value=\"300\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Your top song this week: &quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(song)\" /><text type=\"break\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"50\" endIndex=\"62\" /><option startIndex=\"63\" endIndex=\"65\" /><option startIndex=\"66\" endIndex=\"69\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Your top song this week: \" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Don't stop me now\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>replay_times</code>, followed by <code>&gt;=</code>, and finally <code>300</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: Correct answers",
            "id": 123823,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Code a condition to suggest a restaurant if the user's <code>diet</code> equals <code>vegetarian</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"diet = \" /><text value=\"&quot;vegetarian&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"veggie_restaurant = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Root&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"restaurant = \" /><text value=\"&quot;DelPosto&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" diet == \" /><text value=\"&quot;vegetarian&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\": \" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Try out: &quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(veggie_restaurant)\" /><text type=\"break\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"80\" endIndex=\"82\" /><option startIndex=\"83\" endIndex=\"95\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Try out: \" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Root\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>==</code>, followed by <code>\"vegetarian\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: Wrong answers",
            "id": 123822,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Use <code>!=</code> as a condition to run the code block if <code>today</code> isn't <code>\"Saturday\"</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"today = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Sunday&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" today != \" /><text value=\"&quot;Saturday&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\": \" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Set alarm at 8:00&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"20\" endIndex=\"25\" /><option startIndex=\"26\" endIndex=\"28\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Set alarm at 8:00\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>today</code>, followed by <code>!=</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: Different comparisons",
            "id": 123821,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Use <code>&gt;=</code> to write a condition that checks if the user's <code>age</code> is greater than or equal to <code>18</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"age = \" /><text value=\"20\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"can_drive = \" /><text value=\"False\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" age &gt;= \" /><text value=\"18\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\": \" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  can_drive = \" /><text value=\"True\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(can_drive)\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"31\" endIndex=\"34\" /><option startIndex=\"35\" endIndex=\"37\" /><option startIndex=\"38\" endIndex=\"40\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"True\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>age</code>, followed by <code>&gt;=</code>, and finally <code>18</code>.</p></body></html>"
