            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Store the equality comparison between <code>inbox_full</code> and <code>True</code> inside <code>show_alert</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"inbox_full = \" /><text value=\"True\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"show_alert = inbox_full == \" /><text value=\"True\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" show_alert: \" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Inbox full&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Archive some to continue&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"31\" endIndex=\"49\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"inboxFull != True\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Inbox full\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Archive some to continue\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>inbox_full == True</code>.</p></body></html>"
